		{"id":"x500000000000001","type":"text","text":"### Tools 链\n`.claude/agents/*.md`（6 agent + team-leader 调度规范） · `.claude/rules/*.md`（按需加载） · `.claude/skills/*`（obs / canvas / publish ...） · `.claude/hooks/*`（PreToolUse / UserPromptSubmit / PostToolUse）","x":420,"y":620,"width":700,"height":80,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"a000000000000001","type":"text","text":"# Nova Framework 整体架构\n\n四层结构：**Runtime（AOT 框架）** · **Editor（工具/Inspector/Pipify）** · **Game（业务 DLL，HybridCLR 热更）** · **Minds（Vault 知识库）**。\n\n红线：Runtime ← Editor 单向依赖；Minds 仅约束 NovaFramework.* 程序集；业务 DLL 仅由 ProcedureLoadDll 加载。","x":-1100,"y":-760,"width":2320,"height":140,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"m410000000000001","type":"text","text":"## PARA\n\n`0-Index/` 索引 + AI 协作规则\n`1-Inbox/` AI 草稿\n`2-Areas/` ADR/PAT/GLO/MOC\n`3-Resources/` RES\n`4-Archives/` 废弃归档","x":140,"y":490,"width":340,"height":140,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"m410000000000002","type":"text","text":"## Layer 0/1 索引\n\nLayer 0：`0-Index.md`\nLayer 1：`0-Index-{ADR,PAT,GLO,RES,MOC}.md`（自动生成）","x":500,"y":490,"width":340,"height":140,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"m410000000000003","type":"text","text":"## 21 张 MOC\n\n20 模块 + 1 Workflow；动手前必读对应 MOC（ADR-034/PAT-82）","x":860,"y":490,"width":340,"height":140,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"r110000000000001","type":"text","text":"## Manager 三层链\n\n`ManagerBase` → 模块 Manager（如 `IUIManager`） → 实现类\n\n**Priority** 控盘启停顺序","x":-1080,"y":-490,"width":260,"height":140,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r130000000000002","type":"text","text":"### ObjectPool\nGameObject 池 + `IReference` 纯 C# 池","x":-840,"y":-200,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r120000000000006","type":"text","text":"### Event\n`EventManager` + `EventPool` + `EventData`","x":120,"y":-330,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"m410000000000004","type":"text","text":"## 红线\n\n- AI 仅可写 `1-Inbox/`；`2-Areas/` 经 `/nova-obs inbox-to-areas` 入库；`4-Archives/` 经 `/nova-obs *-to-archives`\n- Minds 作用域仅 `NovaFramework.*` 程序集；业务侧违反不入 obs\n- memory ↔ obs 分工：memory 留指针；obs 留全文；禁互相复制（PAT-17）","x":140,"y":650,"width":1060,"height":140,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"r120000000000001","type":"text","text":"### Asset\nYooAsset 封装；外部统一称\"资源系统\"；Asset 地址 = 资源主键","x":-1080,"y":-330,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r130000000000001","type":"text","text":"### Config / Table\nConfigSO（编辑器→运行时）+ Luban Table","x":-1080,"y":-200,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r120000000000003","type":"text","text":"### Sound / Vibrate / Localization\n表现层三件套","x":-600,"y":-330,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"g310000000000001","type":"text","text":"## 业务 Procedure\n\n`ProcedurePreload` / `ProcedurePlaying` 等；由 `ProcedureLoadDll` 在 dll Load 完成后延迟注册","x":-1020,"y":490,"width":340,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"g310000000000002","type":"text","text":"## 业务 View / Manager\n\n直接继承 MonoBehaviour；Prefab `m_Script` 直挂 dll 类型；`AddComponent` / `Instantiate` 与原生一致","x":-660,"y":490,"width":340,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"g310000000000003","type":"text","text":"## 接入约定\n\nnamespace == asmdef name；命名空间唯一写入 ConfigRuntimeSO；`Assembly.Load` 仅 Util.HybridCLR","x":-300,"y":490,"width":340,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"g310000000000004","type":"text","text":"## 红线\n\n- 业务 DLL 内类名/命名空间重构会让旧 Prefab `m_Script` 全部失效 + 旧 AB 报废\n- `EnableHotfix` 总开关控制 `CheckVersion → Hotfix → AppDownload` 三个 Procedure\n- dll 字节与 AB 共享同一份 YooAsset manifest，原子构建 + 强一致","x":-1020,"y":650,"width":1060,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"r110000000000003","type":"text","text":"## TypeCreator\n\n类型实例化唯一入口；`AddComponent` / `Activator.CreateInstance` 都收口于此","x":-520,"y":-490,"width":260,"height":140,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r110000000000004","type":"text","text":"## Procedure / FSM\n\n`ProcedureBase` + `Fsm`；启动期 6 个内置 Procedure，业务 Procedure 由 `ProcedureLoadDll` 延迟注册","x":-240,"y":-490,"width":260,"height":140,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r110000000000005","type":"text","text":"## Util.HybridCLR\n\n`Assembly.Load` / `LoadMetadataForAOTAssembly` 唯一入口；启动顺序硬约束","x":40,"y":-490,"width":260,"height":140,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r120000000000004","type":"text","text":"### Persist\nSQLite + PlayerPrefs + FileFragment 三后端","x":-360,"y":-330,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r120000000000005","type":"text","text":"### Network\nHTTP + WebSocket + DoH","x":-120,"y":-330,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r120000000000002","type":"text","text":"### UI\nViewBase + Group + Layer；业务类一律 `*View`","x":-840,"y":-330,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r130000000000003","type":"text","text":"### Prefab\n`PrefabManager` + `PrefabInstanceTag`","x":-600,"y":-200,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r130000000000005","type":"text","text":"### Debug\n`DebugComponent` + RuntimeDebugger + DiskChecking","x":-120,"y":-200,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r130000000000004","type":"text","text":"### SDK\n`ISDKPlugin` 抽象 + `SetConfig` 物料注入","x":-360,"y":-200,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r110000000000002","type":"text","text":"## Component 三层链\n\n`ComponentBase` → 模块 Component（如 `UIComponent`）\n\nMonoBehaviour 寄生于 GameObject","x":-800,"y":-490,"width":260,"height":140,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"r130000000000006","type":"text","text":"### App\n`AppVersionResult` + LauncherUI 启动期","x":120,"y":-200,"width":220,"height":110,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"e210000000000001","type":"text","text":"## Inspector\n\n`Editor` + `*.Methods.cs` + `RuntimeDrawer`；**EditorUtil.Draw** 唯一绘制入口","x":500,"y":-470,"width":300,"height":140,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"e210000000000003","type":"text","text":"## Pipify 流水线\n\nRunner + Step + DataPipeline + BuildProcessor；Excel→JSON、代码生成、AB 构建一站式","x":500,"y":-310,"width":300,"height":140,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"e210000000000005","type":"text","text":"## EditorUtil.Draw\n\n业务 Editor 一律调用 `EditorUtil.Draw.*`，**禁止**直调 Unity 原生 `EditorGUI` / `EditorGUILayout` / `GUILayout`；缺接口扩进封装层","x":500,"y":-150,"width":660,"height":140,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"e210000000000002","type":"text","text":"## EditorWindow\n\nConfigWindow / DataWindow / 各模块管理工具；禁用 EditorPrefs（跨项目串味）","x":820,"y":-470,"width":340,"height":140,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"e210000000000004","type":"text","text":"## HybridCLR Editor\n\nDLL 编译 + AOT metadata 拷贝 + YooAsset manifest 同批；UPM 发布脚本","x":820,"y":-310,"width":340,"height":140,"color":"4"}
